  "universalRules": {
    "shortCodeMaxLength": 5,
    "shortCodeAppliesTo": [
      "Department",
      "Designation",
      "Leave Type"
    ],
    "commonActions": [
      "Add New",
      "Edit",
      "Delete",
      "Import from Excel",
      "Export to Excel"
    ],
    "commonFilters": [
      "Include Inactive",
      "Active Only",
      "Inactive Only"
    ],
    "commonOptions": [
      "Use as Default"
    ],
    "formControlNames": {
      "ShortCode": "ShortCode",
      "Name": "Name",
      "Description": "Description"
    }
  },
  "selectors": {
    "addNewButton": "button:has-text(\"Add New\"), button:has-text(\"Add\"), .btn.btn-primary:has-text(\"Add\")",
    "saveButton": "button:has-text(\"Save\"), button:has-text(\"Submit\"), .btn.btn-success:has-text(\"Save\")",
    "updateButton": "button:has-text(\"Update\"), button:has-text(\"Save\"), .btn.btn-success:has-text(\"Update\")",
    "deleteButton": "button:has-text(\"Delete\"), .btn.btn-danger:has-text(\"Delete\"), [title=\"Delete\"]",
    "okButton": "button:has-text(\"Ok\"), button:has-text(\"OK\")",
    "yesButton": "button:has-text(\"Yes\"), button:has-text(\"Confirm\")",
    "searchBox": "input[placeholder*=\"Search\"], input[placeholder*=\"Filter\"]",
    "shortCodeInput": "input[formcontrolname=\"ShortCode\"], input[name=\"Short Code\"]",
    "nameInput": "input[formcontrolname=\"Name\"], input[name=\"Name\"]"
  },
  "template": "### GlobalHR Master Data Rules\nYou are generating automated tests for GlobalHR Cloud Master Data entities.\n\n## UNIVERSAL RULES\n- Short Code fields are limited to 5 characters maximum\n- Short Code applies to: Department, Designation, Leave Type\n- All entities support: Add New, Edit, Delete, Import from Excel, Export to Excel\n- All entities support: Include Inactive / Active Only filters\n- Many entities support: 'Use as Default' option\n\n## ENTITY SPECIFICATIONS\nFor each Master Data entity, use the fields, options, and selectors defined in the entities object.\n\n## CRITICAL BUSINESS RULES\n1. Department requires a Company dropdown selection\n2. Designation requires a Grade dropdown selection\n3. Leave Type has gender-specific options (Maternity for Female, Paternity for Male)\n4. Public Holiday can be generated by year or from government holiday data\n5. GPS Location has two methods: By Map (search + radius) or By Location (country/division/district/township)\n\n## NEGATIVE TEST SCENARIOS\n1. Short Code exceeds 5 characters → should truncate or show validation error\n2. Duplicate Short Code → should show 'already exists' error\n3. Required Name field blank → should show 'required' validation\n4. Delete entity still referenced by other records → should show dependency error"
}